{"tid":2424073,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"印尼15名醫護接種疫苗後確診 部分已打2劑","createTime":"2021-02-26T09:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T03:11:45.000Z","uid":105567,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a00f506201c029c00be3a7890397a8936eb9bc","tid":2424073,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:54:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2887371/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC15%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%20%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B7%B2%E6%89%932%E5%8A%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2887371%2F%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25B0%25BC15%25E5%2590%258D%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%2520%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2589%25932%25E5%258A%2591&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=9e19dad5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2887371/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC15%E5%90%8D%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E5%BE%8C%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%20%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E5%B7%B2%E6%89%932%E5%8A%91</a><br />\n<br />\n《雅加達環球報》（Jakarta Globe）報道，印尼萬丹省南唐格朗市（South Tangerang）衛生部長首長Deden Den宣布，當局接獲報告，指當地一間醫院有15名醫護人員及7名實習生確診感染新冠病毒。他們正接受隔離。<br />\n他稱當中部分人已接種兩劑新冠疫苗，不過確診時間與接種第二劑的時間相隔不到14日，可能未及產生足夠抗體。他拒絕透露已接種兩劑疫苗的確診者具體人數。<br />\n印尼上月13日開始新冠疫苗接種，醫護人員優先注射，至今已有120萬醫護接種了科興研發新冠疫苗。"},{"pid":"dc377416a26b47672fc54fa4d135fc8662872291","tid":2424073,"uid":171845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:55:03.000Z","msg":"成效？？"},{"pid":"18fe379a576af356255f09881f5507bb678334a3","tid":2424073,"uid":120715,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T09:57:43.000Z","msg":"希望香港一班高官打完疫苗後<br />\n面對面近距離探望患有武漢病毒既病人<br />\n俾佢地一個鼓勵<br />\n打嬴依場仗"},{"pid":"bd4f8bae5cfc5a43ae1d0b57da3644ccd56e895a","tid":2424073,"uid":169801,"